    "description": "With 6in1 LEDs, RGBAW + UV LEDs\nEasy control via supplied IR remote control or the integrated display\nMetal bracket for upright and hanging mounting\nIncludes IR remote control for controlling the basic functions\nTechnical specifications:\n\nLight source: 3x 12 Watt RGBAW + UV 6in1 LED\nBeam angle: 25°\nElectronic shutter: 0 - 20 Hz\nElectronic dimmer: 0 - 100%\nControl: DMX (3/4/6/9/11 channels), master / slave, internal programs and color macros, music control\nIndividual colour adjustable on the device\nLC display with four buttons\nDMX input and output: XLR 3-pin\nCurrent input: IEC\nPower supply: 100 - 240 V ~ 50/60 Hz\nPower consumption: max. 36 watts\nHousing made of metal\nDimensions with bracket (W x D x H): 360 x 64 x 150 mm\nWeight: 1.2 kg\n\nUpdated Geometry by BaseTown",
